title: Sweet-Soy Crumbed Chicken & Sesame Kumara with Ponzu Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: Keep chicken strips tender and tasty with an easy sesame coating – just toss it in a quick mix and you’re done! With a
crisp ponzu slaw, roasted sesame kumara and creamy mayo, this family delight combines colours and textures for a
delicious feast!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
